---
title: Smokey Chicken & Garlic Kumara Mash with Roasted Pumpkin & Dill-Parsley Mayo
description: This chicken is glowing with the smokey flavours of our Kiwi spice blend. The sweet and savour kumara mash is a perfect accompaniment, with a tangy herbed mayo to finish things off.
